		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/驱侵之役-水形幻人%B7极旋湍流.assets/Image_16.png')" x="814" y="846" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="67" y="736" width="98" height="26" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="MiSans" fontSize="20" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffbfbf">(N5) <span color="#ffffff">白盾：</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="66" y="634" width="499" height="78" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#7fbfff">1水<span color="#ffffff">盾，击破后消失；允许伤害转换(4倍)；半幻人继承幻人20%的攻击力和12%生命值，每15s生成一只半幻人。<br/></span><span color="#ffbfbf">(N5)</span><span> 12水</span><span color="#ffffff">盾，击破后消失，或被</span><span color="#99ffff">冻结</span><span color="#ffffff">/</span><span color="#ffe599">石化</span><span color="#ffffff">后立即消失；半幻人继承幻人25%的攻击力和12%生命值，每30s生成2只半幻人。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="66" y="858" width="488" height="58" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">场上存在半幻人时，水形幻人会尝试吸收它们，进入15~25s的强化状态， 吸收期间及之后全抗提升<span color="#ffdfbf">45%</span><span>，技能伤害得到提升，<br/></span><span color="#ffbfbf">(N5)</span><span color="#7fbfff"> </span><span>吸收半幻人期间全抗提升</span><span color="#ffdfbf">200%</span><span>，且恢复</span><span color="#ffdfbf">12.5%</span><span>生命值。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="66" y="960" fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff" width="279" height="20" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">水形幻人不会移动，只会待在场地中央。</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1539" y="320" width="432" height="65" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="18" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">幻人扔出纯水制成的标枪，落地造成<span color="#7fbfff">60%</span><span>伤害，并产生内外2层激波，造成</span><span color="#7fbfff">60%</span><span>伤害，可连续施放3次；<br/></span><span color="#9999ff">强化：</span><span>伤害倍率提升，造成</span><span color="#7fbfff">90%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
