		<RichText x="1538" y="512" width="432" height="65" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="18" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">幻人挥舞纯水制成的短刀，进行2次攻击，依次造成<span color="#7fbfff">60%,65%</span><span>伤害；第一段攻击产生剑气，造成</span><span color="#7fbfff">50%</span><span>伤害。<br/></span><span color="#9999ff">强化：</span><span>伤害倍率提升，挥舞造成</span><span color="#7fbfff">90%,95%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/驱侵之役-水形幻人%B7极旋湍流.assets/Image_20.png')" x="1519" y="426">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/驱侵之役-水形幻人%B7极旋湍流.assets/Image_21.png')" x="1396" y="459" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/驱侵之役-水形幻人%B7极旋湍流.assets/Image_22.png')" x="1376" y="438" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="1538" y="704" width="413" height="87" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="18" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">幻人旋转纯水制成的榔锤，进行3次攻击，依次造成<span color="#7fbfff">60%,62.5%,65%</span><span>伤害；第三段攻击产生激波，造成</span><span color="#7fbfff">90%</span><span>伤害。</span><span color="#9999ff">强化：</span><span>伤害倍率提升，挥舞造成</span><span color="#7fbfff">90%,<br/>92.5%,95%</span><span>伤害，不产生激波。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/驱侵之役-水形幻人%B7极旋湍流.assets/Image_23.png')" x="1520" y="617">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/驱侵之役-水形幻人%B7极旋湍流.assets/Image_24.png')" x="1396" y="651" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/驱侵之役-水形幻人%B7极旋湍流.assets/Image_25.png')" x="1376" y="630" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="1538" y="896" width="437" height="108" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="18" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">幻人蓄力，附属<span textDecoration="underline">白盾</span><span>；幻人掀起澜海激潮，在场地内下起小雨，造成</span><span color="#7fbfff">20%</span><span>伤害；12s后白盾消失，溅起的潮水凝结成3把水枪，并一起在自身周围降下，造成</span><span color="#7fbfff">100%</span><span>伤害，并产生一道冲击波引爆所有半幻人，造成</span><span color="#7fbfff">100%</span><span>伤害，冲击波将会</span><span color="#ffbfbf">秒杀</span><span>在场非无敌状态的角色，持续5s。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/驱侵之役-水形幻人%B7极旋湍流.assets/Image_26.png')" x="1519" y="809">
		</BitmapImage>
